		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Multilingualism</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">"Bilingual" redirects here.  For the journal, see <a href="/wiki/Bilingualism_(journal)" title="Bilingualism (journal)" class="mw-redirect">Bilingualism (journal)</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Bilingual_(disambiguation)" title="Bilingual (disambiguation)">Bilingual (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink"><span class="plainlinks selfreference">For multilingualism in Wikipedia, see <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Multilingual_coordination" title="Wikipedia:Multilingual coordination">Wikipedia:Multilingual coordination</a></span></div>
<div class="infobox sisterproject">
<div style="float: left;">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:Wiktionary-logo-en.svg" class="image" title="Wiktionary-logo-en.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Wiktionary-logo-en.svg/50px-Wiktionary-logo-en.svg.png" width="50" height="54" border="0" /></a></div>
</div>
<div style="margin-left: 60px;">Look up <i><b><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/multilingual" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:multilingual">multilingual</a></b>, <b><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/multilingualism" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:multilingualism">multilingualism</a></b></i> in <a href="/wiki/Wiktionary" title="Wiktionary">Wiktionary</a>, the free dictionary.</div>
</div>
<p>The term <b>multilingual</b> can refer to an individual speaker who uses two or more <a href="/wiki/Languages" title="Languages" class="mw-redirect">languages</a>, a community of speakers in which two or more languages are used, or speakers of different languages.</p>
<p>Multilingual speakers outnumber <a href="/wiki/Monolingual" title="Monolingual" class="mw-redirect">monolingual</a> speakers in the world's population.<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
